Interface IdentifiableTypeDescriptor<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DomainType<T>, DomainTypeDescriptor<T>, EmbeddedContainer<T>, ExpressableType<T>, IdentifiableDomainType<T>, IdentifiableType<T>, InheritanceCapable<T>, ManagedDomainType<T>, ManagedType<T>, ManagedTypeDescriptor<T>, Navigable<T>, NavigableContainer<T>, Serializable, SimpleDomainType<T>, SimpleTypeDescriptor<T>, StateArrayContributorContainer, Type<T>, Writeable

    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractEntityTypeDescriptor, AbstractIdentifiableType, SqmPolymorphicRootDescriptor

    public interface IdentifiableTypeDescriptor<T>
extends InheritanceCapable<T>, IdentifiableDomainType<T>
    Hibernate extension SPI for working with IdentifiableType implementations, which includes both mapped-superclasses MappedSuperclassTypeDescriptor and EntityTypeDescriptor
